channel.title: Live: NASCAR Xfinity Racing Series
channel.desc: The Pit Boss/FoodMaxx 250 gets underway from Sonoma Raceway. Road specialist Shane van Gisbergen showcased his affinity for the Chicago Street Course with a second consecutive Xfinity Series victory there July 5. The Kiwi also won in Chicago in 2023.
